===================================================
 ASCII Box NEWS -- history of user-visible changes
===================================================

Release 0.4.0
=============

- Add NEWS
- Split the contents of asciibox.py into a separate script and a package
- Switch the rendering backend from Cairo to PIL
- Add install requirements to ease installation from PyPi with pip
- Fix arrow rendering when they point to a joint (+)

Release 0.3.1
=============

- Fix the version number scheme
- Fix the handling of 'scale' option of reStructuredText directive

Release 0.3
===========

- Add the reStructuredText extension to the asciibox module
- Add a function for registering the reStructuredText extension

Release 0.2
===========

- Add support for text
- Add command line interface
- Add support for SVG rendering
- Add experimental reStructuredText support
- Switch the rendering backend from PIL to Cairo

Release 0.1
===========

- Add support for basic "boxes and arrows" syntax
- Add support for PNG rendering using PIL